	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Recon : loadlevel SCL_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;DebugBook : Act2 --&gt; Tiefling Path&#xD;&#xA;DebugBook : Region --&gt; Act2 --&gt; Haven --&gt; After Checkpoint&#xD;&#xA;Others : Walk to the bar&#xD;&#xA;Recon : oe rolanleaveshaven (if you want to do rolan is missing one-liners)&#xD;&#xA;Recon : oe prisonersreturn (for cal and lia to return to last light)&#xD;&#xA;Recon : SetGlobalOsirisFlag GLO_Prodigy_State_Dead (optional for dead path)&#xD;&#xA;Others : Talk to Cal&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Resuce Cal and/or Lia from Moonrise towers (this dialogue includes solo versions for if Lia died in Moonrise), then speak to Cal in Last Light. If Rolan is present, the reunion dialogue will play first." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="173" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Cal has been rescued from Moonrise Towers by the player and is now in Last Light. This dialogue covers multiple states: Rolan is missing, Rolan is dead, Rolan and Cal had a fight (player must pass a persuade to calm the fight, pass and fail states here), and a general state for when cal, lia and rolan are all alive and well and cal is grateful to the player." />
			<children>
